Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.04,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}One time 構成した世界線を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Loop back なんてあり得ないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:26.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}One life 与えられたスクリプトを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:28.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}派手に躍らせようか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.04,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}少し迷って　I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}軽そうに見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:52.48,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無価値じゃない　Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}どんな未来だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:00.81,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}思い出すべき過去とか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:07.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}存在しないこと知っても構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.41,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:12.01,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:14.83,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}すれ違っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.60,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}絆ほど強さ纏って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.75,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:27.83,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}この声を聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}誇れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.36,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.04,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一次成形的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}已無法再倒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:26.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}被賦予的人生腳本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:28.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}讓其大放異彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.04,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}感到些許迷茫  I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}儘管看似玩世不恭
Comment: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:52.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那並非徒勞  Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無論未來如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:00.81,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那本該喚醒的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:07.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}就算是飄渺的存在又何妨
Comment: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Comment: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:12.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:14.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}即使擦身而過
Comment: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.60,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}如牽掛般縈繞身旁
Comment: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:27.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}能否聽到我的吶喊
Comment: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}引以為傲吧
Comment: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
